Welcome to the AVL video platform
=================================

So, this project is a simple django project that indexes uploaded videos
and, in a near future, will convert videos to some of the most common
formats, like ogv, webm and flv.

This project also provide a very simple to use javascript API that
allows people to embed videos managed by an instance of this software in
any other website.

I'll add more info here soon, I promisse!
